state.name: IPESC Endurance Championship (Season 1)
state.rulesDescription: Championship rules are as per our Regulations found in our official discord server.

generalData.homeContent:
This is the inaugural IPESC 2.4hr Endurance Championship! Weekly 2.4hr multi-class GT3/GT4 endurance racing on Friday nights from 2100 (AEDT). Our first season has the championship racing at the following tracks:

  1. Suzuka

  2. Catalunya

  3. Nurburgring

  4. Kyalami

  5. Brands Hatch

  6. Misano

  7. Imola

  8. Spa

  9. Bathurst

Normally our championship will go for 10 weeks, but for this time of the year, we'll be concluding with the Bathurst 2.4hr endurance race on Friday 17 December.
